<title type="html"><![CDATA[4/6 Addiction/Do Robots Deserve Rights?]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=27&amp;p=31#p31"><![CDATA[
<span style="font-weight: bold">Host: Lyndon</span><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Article 1</span><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Addiction</span><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ao8L-0nSYzg">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ao8L-0nSYzg</a><!-- m --><br /><br />What causes addiction? Easy, right? Drugs cause addiction. But maybe it is not that simple.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Discussion</span><br />1. have you ever get addicted to anything? share with your partner.<br />2. If you have addiction and it's a bad one, how did you quit it? If you didn't quit, share the reason you don't quit.<br />3. After this video, you think the drugs are still problems? or the people who use it are problems? Or both of them are not problems?<br />4. what kinds of life is your &quot;Rat Park&quot;(heaven of rats)? Do you satisfied with your life right now?<br />5. nowadays more and more people become &quot;Phubbers&quot;, do you think they get addiction? if yes, why do you think is the reason to get them addicted?  <br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Article 1<br />Addiction</span><br />Do Robots Deserve Rights? What if Machines Become Conscious?<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DHyUYg8X31c">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DHyUYg8X31c</a><!-- m --><br /><br />What shall we do once machines become conscious? Do we need to grant them rights?<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Discussion</span><br />1. share a movie that impressed you the most and it's about &quot;Robots&quot;.<br />2. what do you think the robots will be like in the future? Will they have self-conscious? If they will, would you like to have one?<br />3. Do you think robots should have right to protect themselves? <br />4. Would you afraid if machines become conscious, why? <br />5. Elon Musk said people can connect our brain to AI (Or upload our conscious to AI or computer) in the future, do you think that will cause the line between robots and human become blurred?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=93">Lyndon</a> — Tue Apr 04, 2017 10:16 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
